description:
After Corbin's adventure with Saber, I knew he could really fuck good.
Someone call Beau!
This time out Beau was way into Corbin, as he turned to me during a transition and said "He tastes as good as he smells!"
"Yeah, I know." I deadpanned back at him.
Corbin's look is evolving. He's added a new tattoo, but has given up on all his piercings, and is in body building "bulking up" phase. He's been real positive and up beat each new time I see him, and sounds like things are going well for him.
This was one of those movies that shot themselves, I just had to stand around and watch them fuck each other. Their energy and enthusiasm is infectious!
Enjoy!
title: Beau & Corbin - Wrapped
